latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Presenting Mood Ring, a Spring-Summer capsule collection inspired from Lorde's 2021 album 'Solar Power' for @san.dressed.you 

Lorde said of the album. “In times of heartache, grief, deep love, or confusion. I’ve learned to breathe out, and tune in. This is what came through."

For Mood Ring, you'll see a three-tiered dutch dress in variations across three versatile silhouettes: Mist, Honey and Rouge. These three pieces are great for your next weekend getaway, an impromptu vacation, a day picnic, or anything you want it to be.

Mood Ring celebrates the feeling of starting again. It is the 'hype-dress' that tells you that you need to do is take that one step and it might just take you places.

Here's to knowing that it is TIME To Start SOMETHING New & trust THE magic of BEGINNINGS.❤️✨

Now showing on:
@simrann97 @nukkuji97 and @raagini_7 for @san.dressed.you
Film and Concept: @simrann97
Styled by: @raagini_7
Thumbnail and Mood: @nukkuji97
